OL,3,CWarning of 'further industrial action'
OL,4,Cafter education unions meet minister
OL,6,FThere has been a warning of further
OL,7,Findustrial action in education as a
OL,8,Fdispute over the pay and grading of
OL,9,Fschool support staff in Northern
OL,10,FIreland continues.
OL,12,FTrade unions representing workers,
OL,13,Fincluding classroom assistants,
OL,14,Fkitchen staff, bus drivers, cleaners
OL,15,Fand administrative workers, met with
OL,16,FStormont Education Minister Paul Givan
OL,17,Fat Stormont on Tuesday.
