OL,3,CWarning of 'further industrial action'
OL,4,Cafter education unions meet minister
OL,6,FThe GMB Union, which represents more
OL,7,Fthan 3,000 school staff in Northern
OL,8,FIreland, said the minister "offered no
OL,9,Fmoney for pay".
OL,11,FThey said he "made it clear that
OL,12,Fwithin the current public sector pay
OL,13,Fbudget of #684 million there was
OL,14,Fnothing to address the pay and grading
OL,15,Freview for school staff, which has
OL,16,Fbeen ongoing since 2018".
OL,18,FGMB said it will consult with members
OL,19,Fwith a view to taking further
OL,20,Findustrial action.
