OL,3,CWarning of 'further industrial action'
OL,4,Cafter education unions meet minister
OL,6,FRegional organiser Jim Donley said his
OL,7,Fmembers across the Education Authority
OL,8,Fare "some of the lowest paid in the
OL,9,Fcountry".
OL,11,F"This news will be another blow to
OL,12,Fworkers who have been campaigning
OL,13,Fsince 2018 for an end to the mismatch
OL,14,Fbetween grades and responsibilities,"
OL,15,Fhe said.
OL,17,F"Previous Stormont Executives have
OL,18,Ffailed to address this ` it simply
OL,19,Fisn't acceptable given the business
OL,20,Fcase has already been agreed between
OL,21,Funions and management.
