OL,3,CWarning of 'further industrial action'
OL,4,Cafter education unions meet minister
OL,6,F"GMB now has no alternative now but to
OL,7,Fengage with our members with the view
OL,8,Fto taking further industrial action."
OL,10,FSpeaking after the meeting, Paul Givan
OL,11,Fsaid: "I have made it clear to JNC
OL,12,Fmembers today that the resolution of
OL,13,Fall industrial action is a priority
OL,14,Ffor me.
OL,16,F"I underlined to unions my gratitude
OL,17,Ffor the contribution made by support
OL,18,Fstaff to the education and lives of
OL,19,Four children and young people.
