OL,3,CWarning of 'further industrial action'
OL,4,Cafter education unions meet minister
OL,6,F"Without their outstanding dedication
OL,7,Fand hard work, those who are most
OL,8,Fdependent on the services they
OL,9,Fprovide, would not receive the vital
OL,10,Fsupport they need and deserve.
OL,12,F"I very much regret the serious impact
OL,13,Fthat strike action is having on the
OL,14,Feducation and wellbeing of children
OL,15,Fand young people across Northern
OL,16,FIreland, most especially those who
OL,17,Fattend our special schools where the
OL,18,Feffect is felt most acutely."
