OL,3,CWarning of 'further industrial action'
OL,4,Cafter education unions meet minister
OL,6,FHe added: "I want all staff in the
OL,7,Feducation sector to be paid at a fair
OL,8,Flevel for the job they do, however
OL,9,Fthere are significant costs associated
OL,10,Fwith a resolution of current strike
OL,11,Faction.
OL,13,F"I am committed to resolving the
OL,14,Fissues around the business case and
OL,15,Fwill be bidding for additional funding
OL,16,Fin Executive's Budget 2024-25 to
OL,17,Fenable the recommendations from the
OL,18,Fpay and grading review to be
OL,19,Fimplemented."
